    "instruction": "Load metric.csv and (1) compute the global P95 threshold for each (cmdb_id, kpi_name) using the full available series, (2) filter metric points to the incident window 2024-01-24 22:18:18 to 2024-01-24 22:48:18 UTC, (3) for each (cmdb_id, kpi_name) produce: total points in-window, count of in-window points > P95, earliest timestamp (UTC) when value > P95 in-window (if any), max value in-window, and the P95 threshold. Return a compact table limited to top 20 groups sorted by count of anomalies desc, with columns: cmdb_id, kpi_name, total_in_window, anomalies_count, earliest_anomaly_timestamp, max_in_window, p95_threshold. If no anomalies found, return the top 20 groups by max_in_window desc instead."
}

