    "analysis": "The previous executor run analyzed metric.csv and found short memory spikes (mem KPI) across many services within the incident window, with earliest breaches clustered around 22:44 UTC (auth had an earlier breach at 22:34). These mem anomalies are transient and only slightly above P95, so we must determine whether they are root-causal or secondary. According to the workflow, next we should inspect traces to see whether service latency or downstream call durations correlate with these memory spikes and to identify the most downstream faulty service. Trace analysis will help decide which service is the root cause among multiple service-level anomalies.",
